                        },
                        {
                          "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
                          "Text": "EccelE, 2012 Meteorol. Appl. 19: 118–128 (2012) p.120: \n\nes = saturation water vapour pressure.  Calculated by a common empirical interpolation function (see, e.g., WMO, 1979; Holbo, 1981\n\n\nes = 6.1078 * exp (17.269 (T /(T + 237.3))",
                          "Name": "Memo",
                          "Children": [],
